title: uberchemist - The Underground Trio - self-titled album - 128kbps
description:
The Underground Trio is a great jazz band that hails from Platteville, WI, USA. My friend Erik knew them all very well and even had them come play some parties at his house. This music is instrumental and varies from track to track; any jazz fan should give this album a listen. A large scan of the album cover art is also included. You will not find this CD in retail stores.
